    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4c.33.15-17_0001" />
                <fw type="curatorial">15</fw>
                <note type="curatorial">Aly Collection
                140-2</note>
                
                <fw type="letterhead">
                Skyrim Farm             <hi rend="caps">JOHN G. NEIHARDT</hi>
                    <lb/>
                Route 7
                    <lb/>
                Columbia, Mo.
                </fw>
                
                <opener>
                <dateline>Aug. 10 '61</dateline>
                
                
                <salute>Dear Lucile:</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>Thanks for the article about us. It isn't bad, is it?</p>
                
                <p>I'm wondering how we can plan to meet during the short while you will have in Columbia I believe there is one train a day each way between here and Centralia </p>
                
                <p>I'll have some letters for you.</p>
                
                <p>Bob Leaf, an old student now in New York, writes me that he is
                    
                    <pb facs="nei.j4c.33.15-17_0002"/>
                    <fw type="curatorial">16</fw>
                    
                    again working on the movies, pushing <hi rend="underline">Three Friends</hi>. He seems hopeful, but I'm not. Still he's a clever chap.</p> 
                
                <p>We were fortunate on the drive home. The high Rockies, of course, were cool, and all the way across Kansas the temperature did not rise above the middle seventies.</p>
                
                <p>It's <hi rend="underline">good</hi> to know you and Bower are through with the big job.</p>
                <closer>
                <salute>Affection for each of you dear ones.</salute>
                    
                    <signed>John N.</signed>
                </closer>
                
                <note type="authorial">Arf! Arf! Arf!</note>
                    
                    
            </div1>
            
            
            
